    <li>Medical Aspirants must achieve at least 50% on a PCB exam. </li>
    <li>Candidates in the SC / ST / OBC category must earn at least 45% points. </li>
    <li>Candidates for admission to the University of Georgia are required to take the NEET exam. </li>
    <li>Students need a passport.</li>
   
