<h3>Admission Procedure for MBBS in Georgia</h3>
<p>If you are seeking MBBS admission in Georgia, it is important that you are familiar with the following admission procedures:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Candidates must fill out the correct details on the online application form in order to study MBBS.  </li>
    <li>After the online application, students must submit the required documents. </li>
    <li>When the documents are complete, you will receive an invitation from the university.  </li>
    <li>The <a href="https://www.nmc.org.in/" target="_blank">NMC</a> will then approve the admission notice. </li>
   
    <li>The selected university will issue an admission notice within 7 business days after the scanned document is checked.</li>
    
    <li>The university will conduct an English efficiency test via a Skype / Zoom meeting. </li>  
    <li>Once you receive your admission letter, you will need to pay the tuition fee to the university bank.</li>  
    <li>After receiving the documents from the university, Kayak Education Services will apply for VISA. </li>  
    <li>This process will take more or less 30-45 days. </li>      
    
</ul>
